        <div>
            <pb facs="#TL-0418.jpg" n="part3_p026.jpg" xml:id="img_0026" corresp="https://id.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/tillich-lectures/part3_p026.jpg"/>
            
            <p facs="#facs_26_tr_2">
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_1" n="N001"/>„
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_2" n="N002"/>in the power of a higher principle. This I would call the negative concept of an education of Kjustment.
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_3" n="N003"/>If we use that term, "education for Kjustment," then we should always read Huxley's Brave New
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_4" n="N004"/> I World in order to see where we can avoid producing "gamma's" in our school's, namely that
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_5" n="N005"/>lowest class of workers which is produced en masse by special means of stimulus and response, and
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_6" n="N006"/>conditioned reflexes. This is of course a.caricature,.but the caricature can become a symbol for
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_7" n="N007"/>a tendency. And 1 am very much afraid that Huxley was right when he wrote this caricature,
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_8" n="N008"/>that this Gendency of the production of gamma's and beta's and alpha's of course—of which the most
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_9" n="N009"/>important is the production of "gamma's" who say "We are proved to be gamma's," namely the
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_10" n="N010"/>lowest—and to take away the attempt to go beyond the lowest by saying No!
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_26_tr_3">
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_1" n="N001"/>Now I only indicate this danger because I believe, with all the other conformist tendencies
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_2" n="N002"/>which come from radio, moving, newspapers, television, etc., there is a real danger of a total Kjustment
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_3" n="N003"/>of Kajustment (in the second sense of the word) which indeed would finally destroy itself because
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_4" n="N004"/>the creative spirit would be driven out. This is the limit of THIS ideal.
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_5" n="N005"/>Then the third ideal is introducing into groups the méaning of which is' expressed in ets of
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_6" n="N006"/>symbols, doctrines, and perhaps dogmas. Introduction is the interpretative introduction into these
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_7" n="N007"/>concepts, doctrines and symbols. This is not necessarily the same as the second is. The education
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_26_tr_1">
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_1" n="N001"/>of Ijustment could be described as patternization, subjection to a pattern. The third can be
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_2" n="N002"/>descdaibed as conformism, to introduce into a group with which one conflicts, without being modelled
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_3" n="N003"/>according to a pattern. But of course there is a similar problem in this introductory type, namely
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_4" n="N004"/>Monsieur,
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_5" n="N005"/>dʼune manière vieuse
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_6" n="N006"/>dʼune manière beaucoup
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_7" n="N007"/>Monsieur
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_8" n="N008"/>dans les
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_9" n="N009"/>dʼacquerir
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_10" n="N010"/>ne pense que vous y avez
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_11" n="N011"/>de Vous avez
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_12" n="N012"/>dans
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_13" n="N013"/>dʼune manière est devenu de ses
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_14" n="N014"/>dʼune manière beaucoup
            </p>
            
